data/seeds.csv
  -> skill-pipeline source-discover --deal <slug>     (optional)
  -> skill-pipeline raw-fetch --deal <slug>
  -> raw/<slug>/*
  -> skill-pipeline preprocess-source --deal <slug>
  -> data/deals/<slug>/source/*
  -> skill-pipeline compose-prompts --deal <slug>

